    <h2 class="title" data-i18n="term.title">Even full-screen TUIs.</h2>
    <p class="lead" data-i18n="term.lead">Paste or <code>vgrab</code> colored terminal output — and now full-screen apps like <code>htop</code>, <code>lazygit</code>, and Neovim too. Vitrine reconstructs the final screen — every cursor move and color, wide CJK and emoji included — in your theme.</p>
